{"tid":1911844,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聶德權：政府往後會分批將仍在湖北的三千多名港人接回港","createTime":"2020-03-05T15:23:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T00:56:21.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"32cbb68bf5b8089dc8b299b4ed1662fdee0ff4e6","tid":1911844,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:23:12.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】政制及內地事務局局長聶德權隨武漢包機抵港後指，首階段四架包機共接回469名港人，較早前預計少了64人，當中6人未能通過體溫檢測。<span style=\"color: red;\">現時仍有逾三千港人滯留湖北不同地點</span>，政府會視乎情況，分批按緩急先後接他們回港。<br />\n<br />\n政制及內地事務局局長聶德權：「湖北省不同地區，有超過三千九百人，減了這兩天接回來的四百多人，仍然有相當的數目，往後我們會用分批，按照緩急先後及實際可行性原則處理。我們尋求一個實際、可行及穩妥的方案時，需要考慮及顧及內地及香港疫情的發展，需要考慮本港檢疫及醫療系統的承受能力，我們需要密切監察首批港人接受檢疫的情況。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=383171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D383171&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaqx0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=2581457c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D383171&h=d84c3fb3\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=383171</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1243ec2a8628682d5d63e30135f4e52d40515f2","tid":1911844,"uid":83609,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:23:59.000Z","msg":"有無咁多香港人喺嗰度呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d578c4a1399b6ccd5cde368748259da62913f59","tid":1911844,"uid":304769,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:24:46.000Z","msg":"香港撤僑<br />\n推到微博暴動<br />\n<br />\n想消滅支那，我們就要帶領支畜暴動和革命，才有機會從內部瓦解支共（輸出革命+加速主義，缺一不可）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1911527\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1911527</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n（國際戰線）借助日韓爆發武肺推動全球反奶共運動和全球排支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1894747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0bc8a086806e15fdc4cde184a9a4cf866318aac7","tid":1911844,"uid":26333,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:25:24.000Z","msg":"又多左一千<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebb8e61fb1d1511f1e12846bb8b458b40a1743cc","tid":1911844,"uid":225130,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:27:24.000Z","msg":"一批批搞掂先比下一批<br />\n個dd死左都未番到黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b098b9d2bd0568db5109cdf9704a53cbfdeb834","tid":1911844,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0bc8a086806e15fdc4cde184a9a4cf866318aac7","tid":1911844,"uid":26333,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:25:24.000Z","msg":"又多左一千<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:27:31.000Z","msg":"原本冇咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac9026205cdae605093d743512c1624ec50e090d","tid":1911844,"uid":225130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0b098b9d2bd0568db5109cdf9704a53cbfdeb834","tid":1911844,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0bc8a086806e15fdc4cde184a9a4cf866318aac7","tid":1911844,"uid":26333,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:25:24.